[
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1988年数学（一）真题解析",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            280,
            85,
            716,
            114
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            59,
            136,
            90,
            149
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【解】 由 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{1}{(n + 1)\\cdot 3^{n + 1}}\\Bigg{/}\\frac{1}{n\\cdot 3^n} = \\frac{1}{3}$ ，得收敛半径 $R = 3$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            154,
            716,
            189
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $x - 3 = -3$ ，即 $x = 0$ 时， $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{(-1)^n}{n}$ 收敛；",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            196,
            479,
            226
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $x - 3 = 3$ ，即 $x = 6$ 时， $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{1}{n}$ 发散，",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            236,
            423,
            266
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故级数 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{(x-3)^n}{n \\cdot 3^n}$ 的收敛域为 $[0,6)$ .",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            275,
            409,
            305
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【解】 由 $\\mathrm{e}^{\\varphi^2 (x)} = 1 - x$ ，得 $\\varphi (x) = \\sqrt{\\ln(1 - x)}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            316,
            512,
            333
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $1 - x \\geqslant 1$ 得 $\\varphi(x)$ 的定义域为 $(- \\infty, 0]$ .",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            340,
            454,
            352
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【解】 由高斯公式得",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            360,
            268,
            376
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} I = \\oiint_ {S} x ^ {3} d y d z + y ^ {3} d z d x + z ^ {3} d x d y = 3 \\iiint_ {a} (x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}) d v \\\\ = 3 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} d \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} d \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {1} r ^ {4} \\sin \\varphi d r = \\frac {6 \\pi}{5} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\sin \\varphi d \\varphi = \\frac {1 2 \\pi}{5}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            206,
            383,
            702,
            446
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            59,
            455,
            148,
            470
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $(1 + 2t)\\mathrm{e}^{2t}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            475,
            264,
            492
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f(t) = \\lim_{x\\to \\infty}t\\left(1 + \\frac{1}{x}\\right)^{2tx} = t\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left[\\left(1 + \\frac{1}{x}\\right)^x\\right]^{2t} = te^{2t},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            497,
            609,
            526
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $f^{\\prime}(t) = \\mathrm{e}^{2t} + 2t\\mathrm{e}^{2t} = (1 + 2t)\\mathrm{e}^{2t}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            533,
            394,
            549
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $\\frac{3}{2}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            558,
            202,
            585
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f(x)$ 的傅里叶级数在 $x = 1$ 处收敛于",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            594,
            466,
            608
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {f (1 - 0) + f (1 + 0)}{2} = \\frac {f (1 - 0) + f (- 1 + 0)}{2} = \\frac {1 + 2}{2} = \\frac {3}{2}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            250,
            615,
            770,
            645
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{12}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            654,
            200,
            680
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\int_0^{x^3 -1}f(t)\\mathrm{d}t = x$ 两边对 $x$ 求导得 $3x^{2}f(x^{3} - 1) = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            686,
            592,
            713
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "取 $x = 2$ 得 $f(7) = \\frac{1}{12}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            724,
            293,
            749
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 40.",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            759,
            192,
            773
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由 $\\mathbf{A} + \\mathbf{B} = (\\pmb {\\alpha} + \\pmb {\\beta},2\\pmb{\\gamma}_2,2\\pmb{\\gamma}_3,2\\pmb{\\gamma}_4)$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            780,
            464,
            793
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\left| \\boldsymbol {A} + \\boldsymbol {B} \\right| = \\left| \\boldsymbol {\\alpha} + \\boldsymbol {\\beta}, 2 \\gamma_ {2}, 2 \\gamma_ {3}, 2 \\gamma_ {4} \\right| = 8 \\left| \\boldsymbol {\\alpha} + \\boldsymbol {\\beta}, \\gamma_ {2}, \\gamma_ {3}, \\gamma_ {4} \\right| \\\\ = 8 \\left(\\left| \\boldsymbol {\\alpha}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {2}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {3}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {4} \\right| + \\left| \\boldsymbol {\\beta}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {2}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {3}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {4} \\right|\\right) = 8 \\left(\\left| \\boldsymbol {A} \\right| + \\left| \\boldsymbol {B} \\right|\\right) = 4 0. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            97,
            802,
            698,
            836
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "三、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            59,
            843,
            146,
            858
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            864,
            204,
            878
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $f(x)$ 在 $x = x_0$ 处可导，所以 $f(x)$ 在 $x = x_0$ 处可微，",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            886,
            652,
            900
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $\\mathrm{dy} = f^{\\prime}(x_0)\\Delta x = \\frac{1}{2}\\Delta x$ ，故函数在 $x = x_0$ 处的微分 $\\mathrm{dy}$ 是与 $\\Delta x$ 同阶而非等价的无穷小，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            908,
            929,
            934
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（2）【答案】（A）.",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            71,
            210,
            85
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】将 $x = x_0$ 代入 $y'' - 2y' + 4y = 0$ ，得 $f''(x_0) - 2f'(x_0) + 4f(x_0) = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            92,
            756,
            107
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "从而 $f^{\\prime \\prime}(x_0) = -4f(x_0) < 0$ ，由极值判别法得 $x = x_{0}$ 为 $f(x)$ 的极大值点，应选(A).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            114,
            807,
            128
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            138,
            208,
            152
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由奇偶性得",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            160,
            252,
            174
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\iiint_{\\Omega_1}x\\mathrm{d}v = \\iiint_{\\Omega_1}y\\mathrm{d}v = 0,\\quad \\iiint_{\\Omega_1}z\\mathrm{d}v = 4\\iiint_{\\Omega_2}z\\mathrm{d}v,\\quad \\iiint_{\\Omega_1}xyz\\mathrm{d}v = 0$ 显然选(C). ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            179,
            669,
            218
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 （B）.",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            222,
            208,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 因为级数 $\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}a_n(x - 1)^n$ 在 $x = -1$ 处收敛，",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            247,
            520,
            278
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所以其收敛半径 $R \\geqslant |-1 - 1| = 2$ .",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            283,
            392,
            297
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $x = 2$ 时，因为 $|2 - 1| = 1 < R$ ，所以该级数在 $x = 2$ 处绝对收敛，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            305,
            750,
            319
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            327,
            208,
            341
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 方法一",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            349,
            214,
            363
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "若 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\dots ,\\alpha_{s}$ 线性相关，则存在不全为零的数 $k_{1},k_{2},\\dots ,k_{s}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            370,
            603,
            385
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "使得 $k_{1}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} + k_{2}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} + \\dots +k_{s}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{s} = \\mathbf{0},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            394,
            559,
            408
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "不妨设 $k_{1} \\neq 0$ ，则 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = -\\frac{k_{2}}{k_{1}}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} - \\dots - \\frac{k_{s}}{k_{1}}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{s}$ ，即至少有一个向量可由其余向量线性表示，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            417,
            820,
            446
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\dots ,\\alpha_{s}$ 线性无关的充分必要条件是 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\dots ,\\alpha_{s}$ 中任意一个向量都不可由其余向量线性表示，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            455,
            935,
            492
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            500,
            154,
            514
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}$ , 显然 $2\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} + \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} - \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3} \\neq \\mathbf{0}$ 且其中任两个向量线性无关, 但向量组 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}$ 线性相关, 排除(A), (B);",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            522,
            935,
            603
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}$ , 显然 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}$ 不可由 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}$ 线性表示, 但 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}$ 线性相关, 排除(C), 应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            612,
            935,
            691
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "四、【解】 $\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x} = f^{\\prime}\\left(\\frac{x}{y}\\right) + g\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right) - \\frac{y}{x} g^{\\prime}\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right),$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            701,
            466,
            728
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {\\partial^ {2} u}{\\partial x ^ {2}} = \\frac {1}{y} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) - \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) + \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) + \\frac {y ^ {2}}{x ^ {3}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) = \\frac {1}{y} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) + \\frac {y ^ {2}}{x ^ {3}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            735,
            789,
            766
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {\\partial^ {2} u}{\\partial x \\partial y} = - \\frac {x}{y ^ {2}} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) + \\frac {1}{x} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) - \\frac {1}{x} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) - \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) = - \\frac {x}{y ^ {2}} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) - \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            775,
            836,
            806
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $x\\frac{\\partial^2u}{\\partial x^2} +y\\frac{\\partial^2u}{\\partial x\\partial y} = \\frac{x}{y} f''\\left(\\frac{x}{y}\\right) + \\frac{y^2}{x^2} g''\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right) - \\frac{x}{y} f''\\left(\\frac{x}{y}\\right) - \\frac{y^2}{x^2} g''\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right) = 0.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            814,
            727,
            843
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "五、【解】 特征方程为 $\\lambda^2 - 3\\lambda + 2 = 0$ ，特征根为 $\\lambda_1 = 1, \\lambda_2 = 2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            853,
            607,
            867
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$y^{\\prime \\prime} - 3y^{\\prime} + 2y = 0$ 的通解为 $y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            876,
            487,
            890
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设原方程的特解为 $y_0(x) = ax\\mathrm{e}^x$ ，代入得 $a = -2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            899,
            516,
            912
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故原方程的通解为 $y = C_{1} \\mathrm{e}^{x} + C_{2} \\mathrm{e}^{2x} - 2x \\mathrm{e}^{x}$ ( $C_{1}, C_{2}$ 为任意常数).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            922,
            636,
            936
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为曲线 $y = y(x)$ 经过点(0,1)，所以 $C_1 + C_2 = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            71,
            526,
            85
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$y = y(x)$ 在 $x = 0$ 处切线的斜率为 $k = (2x - 1)\\mid_{x = 0} = -1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            94,
            611,
            107
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又由 $y' = C_1 e^x + 2C_2 e^{2x} - 2(x + 1) e^x$ ，得 $C_1 + 2C_2 - 2 = -1$ ，即 $C_1 + 2C_2 = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            116,
            762,
            128
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "从而 $C_1 = 1, C_2 = 0$ ，故所求函数为 $y = (1 - 2x)\\mathrm{e}^x$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            139,
            524,
            150
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "六、【解】设 $M(x,y)$ ，则 $\\overrightarrow{MA} = \\{-x,1 - y\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            161,
            448,
            177
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\overrightarrow {M A} ^ {0} = \\boldsymbol {F} ^ {0} = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + (1 - y) ^ {2}}} \\{- x, 1 - y \\},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            186,
            458,
            218
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $F(x,y) = |F|\\cdot F^0 = \\frac{k}{[x^2 + (1 - y)^2]^{\\frac{3}{2}}}\\{-x,1 - y\\} ,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            229,
            568,
            265
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设 $M$ 沿 $y = \\sqrt{2x - x^2}$ 从点 $B(2,0)$ 到点 $O(0,0)$ 的有向曲线段为 $L$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            276,
            667,
            290
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $W = k\\int_{L}\\frac{-x\\mathrm{d}x + (1 - y)\\mathrm{d}y}{[x^2 + (1 - y)^2]^{\\frac{3}{2}}},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            300,
            367,
            337
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $P(x,y) = -\\frac{x}{[x^2 + (1 - y)^2]^{\\frac{3}{2}}},$ $Q(x,y) = \\frac{1 - y}{[x^2 + (1 - y)^2]^{\\frac{3}{2}}},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            348,
            650,
            384
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = \\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial y}$ 所以曲线积分与路径无关，",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            392,
            431,
            421
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
